ADMP Astroboy56 and Perma Pumpers Perhaps you mean wellbut that article is nearly a month old and it did NOTHING price wise Frankly I think you need to come to grips with the reality of the situation and by every pragmatic factor the situation is dire This stock has had negative ROI for 12 years It is down about 45ths of its preapproval price Sales remain a mystery No upfront Dilution No retail launch Not even a date for such a launch You are entitled to have faith but it is quite misguided and posting silly stuff about Monday and stuffwellthey are your photons I supposebut its misleading to newbies Buy all you want Pump all you want Its not going to make any difference They do not seem willing or able to launch the one items in their inventory that has any value and dilution looms Good luckbut keep your expectations low
